早在[[主要攝影|主要攝影]]前，尼可拉·溫丁·黑芬就到[[第63屆坎城影展|第63屆坎城影展]]上努力銷售《落日車神》的版權，並也釋出了這部片的宣傳海報<ref name="indieWire1" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.totalfilm.com/news/bronson-helmer-fancies-wonder-woman |first=Emma |last=Didbin |title=Bronson helmer fancies Wonder Woman |work={{le|Total Film|Total Film}} |publisher=[[Future_plc|Future Publishing]] |date=2010-05-19 |accessdate=2011-07-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120131184442/http://www.totalfilm.com/news/bronson-helmer-fancies-wonder-woman |archivedate=2012-01-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/promo-poster-nicolas-winding-refns-drive |title=Promo Poster: Nicolas Winding Refn's Drive |first=Peter |last=Sciretta |publisher=Peter Sciretta |work={{le|/Film|/Film}} |date=2010-05-17 |accessdate=2011-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715180259/http://www.slashfilm.com/promo-poster-nicolas-winding-refns-drive/ |archivedate=2011-07-15 }}</ref>。2010年11月，{{le|FilmDistrict|FilmDistrict}}買下了電影的北美發行權<ref name="Deadline1">{{cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/11/filmdistrict-drives-first-big-afm-deal |first=Mike |last=Fleming |title=FilmDistrict Drives To First Big AFM Deal |work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |publisher={{le|Mail.com Media|Mail.com Media Corporation}} |date=2010-09-03 |accessdate=2011-07-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110628083249/http://www.deadline.com/2010/11/filmdistrict-drives-first-big-afm-deal/ |archivedate=2011-06-28 }}</ref>。業主們希望能開始談判購買它之前看到任何鏡頭，以相信電影可以吸引那些喜歡該流派電影的人及藝術家<ref name="WSJ">{{cite news |url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2011/05/20/filmdistrict-and-ryan-gosling-mix-art-with-action-in-drive |title=FilmDistrict and Ryan Gosling Mix Art with Action in "Drive" |first=Anthony |last=Kaufman |work=The Wall Street Journal |publisher=Dow Jones & Company, Inc |date=2011-05-20 |accessdate=2011-07-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110525021127/http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2011/05/20/filmdistrict-and-ryan-gosling-mix-art-with-action-in-drive/ |archivedate=2011-05-25 }}</ref>。《落日車神》定於2011年9月16日在美國上映<ref name="Deadline1" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/2010/12/nicolas-winding-refns-drive-will-hit-theaters-september-16-2011-via-film-district-121316/ |first=Edward |last=Davis |title=Nicolas Winding Refn's ''Drive'' Will Hit Theaters September 16, 2011 Via Film District |work=indieWire |publisher=SnagFilms |date=2010-12-12 |accessdate=2011-07-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170418081852/http://www.indiewire.com/2010/12/nicolas-winding-refns-drive-will-hit-theaters-september-16-2011-via-film-district-121316/ |archivedate=2017-04-18 }}</ref>。

該片於2011年5月20日在[[第64屆坎城影展|第64屆坎城影展]]上首映<ref name="TGCannes"/>。在第一次向媒體展示的時，電影獲得了許多的讚譽<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/early-buzz-nicolas-winding-refns-drive |title=Early Buzz: Nicolas Winding Refn's ''Drive'' Earns Cannes Praise |first=Russ |last=Fischer |work={{le|/Film|/Film}} |publisher=Peter Sciretta |date=2011-05-19 |accessdate=2011-06-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110622011059/http://www.slashfilm.com/early-buzz-nicolas-winding-refns-drive/ |archivedate=2011-06-22 }}</ref>，並獲得了「影展的一些最佳反響」<ref>{{cite news |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2011/05/ryan-gosling-drive-nicolas-refn-james-sallis.html |title=Cannes 2011: With Ryan Gosling's ''Drive'', a different Dane gets his moment |first=Steven |last=Zeitchik |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |date=2011-05-19 |accessdate=2011-07-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110525004855/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2011/05/ryan-gosling-drive-nicolas-refn-james-sallis.html |archivedate=2011-05-25 |df= }}</ref>。《[[衛報|衛報]]》的贊·布洛克斯給了電影好評，但認為它無法贏的坎城的獎項<ref name="Style">{{cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2011/05/20/us-cannes-ryangosling-idUSTRE74J3EC20110520 |title=Blood, fuel power Gosling debut at Cannes festival |first=Nick |last=Vinocur |work=Reuters |publisher=Thomson Reuters |date=2011-05-20 |accessdate=2011-07-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110628190826/https://www.reuters.com/article/2011/05/20/us-cannes-ryangosling-idUSTRE74J3EC20110520 |archivedate=2011-06-28 }}</ref>。他認為，電影中有許多復古感，並就像是《[[生命樹_(電影)|生命樹]]》和《[[世紀末婚禮|世紀末婚禮]]》那樣的偉大藝術和強大的社會評論<ref name="TGCannes" />。部分媒體和觀眾也為片中的極端暴力發出歡呼<ref name="VS" /><ref name="Salon" /> 。《落日車神》獲得了台下觀眾長達15分鐘的[[起立致敬|起立鼓掌]]<ref name="DLH">{{cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/05/cannes-sean-goes-glam-uma-goes-awol-sarkozy-film-sold-to-u-s |title=Cannes: Sean Goes Glam Rock, Uma Leaves Town, Sarkozy Film Sold To U.S. |work=Deadline Hollywood |publisher=Mail.com Media Corporation |first=Pete |last=Hammond |date=2011-05-20 |accessdate=2011-07-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110625105336/http://www.deadline.com/2011/05/cannes-sean-goes-glam-uma-goes-awol-sarkozy-film-sold-to-u-s/ |archivedate=2011-06-25 }}</ref>。黑芬也在該影展上贏得了[[最佳導演獎_(坎城影展)|最佳導演獎]]<ref name="CannesBestDirector">{{cite news |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/ct-live-0523-talking-pictures-cannes-20110522,0,7664199.column |first=Michael |last=Phillips |title=''Tree of Life'' triumphs at Cannes |work=[[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] |publisher=Tribune Company |date=2011-05-22 |accessdate=2011-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110528073559/http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/ct-live-0523-talking-pictures-cannes-20110522%2C0%2C7664199.column |archivedate=2011-05-28 }}</ref>。

