== 反響 ==
=== 評價 ===
[[File:Nicolas_Winding_Refn_Deauville_2011.jpg|right]]
《落日車神》獲得的評價以正面居多。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於239條評論，新鮮度達92%，平均得分8.3／10；該網站共識：「由於其超風格化的暴力、音樂和驚人的畫面，《落日車神》代表完全實現了{{le|藝術動作片|Arthouse action film|藝術動作}}的願景。」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/drive_2011/ |title=''Drive'' Reviews Rotten Tomatoes |author= |work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher=[[Warner_Bros.|Warner Bros.]] |accessdate=2013-09-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928091439/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/drive_2011/ |archivedate=2013-09-28 }}</ref>在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，根據43位評論家而獲得了78分（滿分100），這代表著「普遍讚譽」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/drive |title=Metacritic ''Drive'' Reviews |author= |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=2012-01-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120107045310/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/drive |archivedate=2012-01-07 }}</ref>。而電影也被許多影評人的年末十大榜單中排名最高、項目最多的電影之一。據Metacritic統計的十大榜單中，《落日車神》被列為該年度第四佳的電影，位於《[[生命樹_(電影)|生命樹]]》、《[[大藝術家|大藝術家]]》和《[[世紀末婚禮|世紀末婚禮]]》之後<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.metacritic.com/feature/movie-critic-best-of-2011-top-ten-lists |title=2011 Film Critic Top Ten Lists |author= |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS Interactive]] |date=2012-09-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510134309/http://www.metacritic.com/feature/movie-critic-best-of-2011-top-ten-lists |archivedate=2017-05-10 |accessdate=2017-07-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://moviecitynews.com/2012/01/125132/ |title=2011 Film Critic Top Ten Lists |work=Movie City News |date=2012-01-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120901115907/http://moviecitynews.com/2012/01/125132/ |archivedate=2012-09-01 |access-date=2017-07-13 }}</ref>。

《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》的作家將《落日車神》列為2011年的頭號電影<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.empireonline.com/features/films-of-the-year-2011/p20 |title=Empire's Top 20 Films of 2011 |author= |work=[[帝國雜誌|Empire]] |date=2011-12-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515115210/http://www.empireonline.com/features/films-of-the-year-2011/p20 |archivedate=2013-05-15 |accessdate=2017-07-13 }}</ref>。《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]》的[[彼得·崔維斯|彼得·崔維斯]]給了電影4星的滿分，他認為電影是「一塊輝煌的骯髒生意」，「黑芬是名偉大的藝術家，融合了鐵漢柔情與這些神秘的技能，他當之無愧地贏得了坎城影展最佳導演獎。」崔維斯還說：「準備被[[艾伯特·布魯克斯|艾伯特·布魯克斯]]嚇壞。」他很讚賞布魯克斯的演出，他帶有黑色幽默和冰冷的威脅（以他使用刀刃這點來看），他憑這部2011年電影值得一座[[奧斯卡獎|奧斯卡獎]]<ref name="rollingstone">{{cite news |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/drive-20110908 |first=Peter |last=Travers |title=''Drive'' (R) |work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]] |publisher=Wenner Media LLC |date=2011-09-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110923161517/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/drive-20110908 |archivedate=2011-09-23 |accessdate=2017-07-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/lists/10-best-movies-of-2011-20111207/drive-19691231 |first=Peter |last=Travers |title= 10 Best Movies of 2011 |work=Rolling Stone |publisher=Wenner Media LLC |date=2011-09-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130624130929/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/lists/10-best-movies-of-2011-20111207/drive-19691231 |archivedate=2013-06-24 |accessdate=2017-07-13 }}</ref>。《[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]》的{{le|喬·摩根斯坦|Joe Morgenstern}}也對布魯克斯表示讚賞，稱他的表演是「聳人聽聞」的<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.wsj.com/article/SB10001424053111903927204576572542212463116.html?mod=WSJ_ArtsEnt_LifestyleArtEnt_2|first=Joe| last=Morgenstern| title=Wall Street Journal Review Drive |work=[[華爾街日報|The Wall Street Journal]] |publisher={{le|Sun-Times Media Group|Sun-Times Media Group|Sun-Times Media}} |date=2011-09-14}}</ref>。《[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]》的詹姆斯·羅奇給了《落日車神》一個A的評價，並認為《落日車神》證明了對於一個真正的人才來說，攝影機、娛樂和藝術都是自己的盟友<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/cannes_review_nicolas_winding_refns_drive_starring_ryan_gosling_is |first=James |last=Rocchi |title=Nicholas Winding Refn's  Low-Slung  '80's Crime Drama ''Drive'' has a Dark Majesty |work=[[Indiewire|The Playlist]] |date=2011-09-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130731033549/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/cannes_review_nicolas_winding_refns_drive_starring_ryan_gosling_is |archivedate=2013-07-31 |access-date=2017-07-13 }}</ref>。羅奇也將《落日車神》列為2011年的第一名電影<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.alumni.westernu.ca/alumni-gazette/winter-2012/top-ten-movies-of-2011.html?referrer=https://www.google.com.ph/ |first=James |last=Rocchi |title=Top 10 of films of 2011 |work=Alumni Gazette |publisher=[[西安大略大學|Western University]] |year=2012 |accessdate=2012-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730020711/http://www.alumni.westernu.ca/alumni-gazette/winter-2012/top-ten-movies-of-2011.html?referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.ph%2F |archive-date=2017-07-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

《{{le|Movieline|Movieline}}》的{{le|史蒂芬妮·夏克瑞|Stephanie Zacharek}}稱讚了電影中的動作，並寫到：「在反主流動作電影的所有當前趨勢中，《落日車神》的拍攝與剪輯編排有著外科醫生般的清晰和準確。黑芬並沒把這些行為來愚弄我們，好使人認為這是更令人興奮的。」她也稱讚了黑芬對於電影中的暴力的處理技巧，以及葛斯林和墨里根間低調的浪漫史。她給電影的分數為9.5／10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://movieline.com/2011/09/15/review-ryan-gosling-is-the-goslingest-in-superb-70s-inflected-drive/ |first=Stephanie |last=Zacharek |title=Movieline ''Drive'' Review |work={{le|Movieline|Movieline}} |publisher={{le|Penske Media Corporation|Penske Media Corporation}} |date=2011-09-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130330064039/http://movieline.com/2011/09/15/review-ryan-gosling-is-the-goslingest-in-superb-70s-inflected-drive/ |archivedate=2013-03-30 |accessdate=2017-07-13 }}</ref>。[[羅傑·伊伯特|羅傑·伊伯特]]將《落日車神》排於2011年最佳電影的第七位。他寫道：「這是一部尊重編劇、表演和工藝的電影。它尊重著知識淵博的電影觀眾。」同時也和夏克瑞一樣，稱讚了電影中的動作編排未依賴於CGI技術<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/drive-2011 |first=Roger |last=Ebert |authorlink=Roger Ebert |title=''Drive'' Review |work=[[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]] |publisher=Sun-Times Media |date=2011-09-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202061536/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/drive-2011 |archivedate=2017-02-02 |df= |accessdate=2017-07-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://blogs.suntimes.com/ebert/2011/12/the_best_films_of_2011.html |first=Roger |last=Ebert |authorlink=Roger Ebert |title=Roger Ebert's  Top Ten Films of 2011 |work=[[芝加哥太陽報|Chicago Sun-Times]] |date=2011-12-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120105215412/http://blogs.suntimes.com/ebert/2011/12/the_best_films_of_2011.html |archivedate=2012-01-05 |accessdate=2017-07-13 }}</ref>。

反之，《[[紐約客|紐約客]]》的{{le|安東尼·萊恩|Anthony Lane}}給了電影負面的評價，他認為「《落日車神》的暴力太過寫實了，這最終對電影是不利的。」在提到暴力時，他說：「在抓住我們的注意力的時候，他把它從重要的角度轉移出去。恐怖徘徊和滲透著；其感覺都被吸走了。」<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.newyorker.com/arts/critics/cinema/2011/09/26/110926crci_cinema_lane |first=Anthony |last=Lane |title=Road Kill |work=[[紐約客|The New Yorker]] |publisher=[[康泰納仕|Condé Nast]] |date=2011-09-26 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130131042318/http://www.newyorker.com/arts/critics/cinema/2011/09/26/110926crci_cinema_lane |archivedate=2013-01-31 |accessdate=2017-07-13 }}</ref>《[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]》的{{le|麥可·菲利普斯 (評論家)|Michael Phillips (critic)|麥可·菲利普斯}}也感到有同樣的感覺，雖然他早期是喜歡這部電影的，但《落日車神》仍成了「一個又一個的華麗虐待集」此外，菲利普斯認為這部電影太多依賴於「風格化」，沒有足夠的實質感<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2011-09-15/entertainment/sc-mov-0913-drive-20110915_1_getaway-driver-stunt-driver-refn |first=Michael |last=Phillips |title=''Drive'': Noir  Lives, Dies by Its Looks |work=[[芝加哥論壇報|Los Angeles Times]] |publisher={{le|Tribune Media|Tribune Media|Tribune Company}} |date=2011-09-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513001800/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2011-09-15/entertainment/sc-mov-0913-drive-20110915_1_getaway-driver-stunt-driver-refn |archivedate=2013-05-13 |accessdate=2017-07-13 }}</ref>。2014年，《[[哈芬登郵報|哈芬登郵報]]》將《落日車神》列在過去十五年來超級高估名單中的第八部電影<ref>{{cite news |title=8 Movies From The Last 15 Years That Are Super Overrated |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/06/12/overrated-movies_n_5481916.html |accessdate=2017-05-20 |work=[[哈芬登郵報|The Huffington Post]] |publisher=[[美國線上|AOL]] |date=2014-06-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170225102940/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/06/12/overrated-movies_n_5481916.html |archivedate=2017-02-25 }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾在A+至F間給的評價落在「C-」；因為行銷的誤導，使得觀眾尷尬地預期片中會有更多的飛車和動作戲<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/mike-ryan/the-purge-box-office_b_3415384.html |work=[[哈芬登郵報|The Huffington Post]] |first=Mike |last=Ryan |title=Here's Why You Hated ''The Purge'' |date=2013-06-10 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131009205534/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/mike-ryan/the-purge-box-office_b_3415384.html |archivedate=2013-10-09 |accessdate=2017-07-13 }}</ref>。

