《落日車神》在[[英國電影學院獎|英國電影學院獎]]上提名了四個獎項，其中包括[[英國電影學院獎最佳影片|最佳影片]]、[[英國電影學院獎最佳導演|最佳導演]]、[[英國電影學院獎最佳女配角|最佳女配角]]（凱莉·墨里根）和{{le|英國電影學院獎最佳剪輯|BAFTA Award for Best Editing|最佳剪輯}}。2011年，該片為影評團體中提名數最多的電影之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bafta.org/press/2012-film-awards-nominations,177,SNS.html |author= |title=Nominations Announced for the Orange British Academy Film Award in 2012 |work=BAFTA.org |date=2012-01-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120119214802/http://www.bafta.org/press/2012-film-awards-nominations%2C177%2CSNS.html |archivedate=2012-01-19 |accessdate=2017-07-13 }}</ref><ref name="auto">{{cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/a-complete-guide-to-2011-12-awards-season |first=Peter |last=Knegt |title=A Complete Guide to 2011–12 awards Season |work=Indiewire |publisher=Los Angeles Times |date=2011-09-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121116161149/http://www.indiewire.com/article/a-complete-guide-to-2011-12-awards-season |archivedate=2012-11-16 |accessdate=2017-07-13 }}</ref>。艾伯特·布魯克斯獲得了最多影評團體的提名<ref name="auto"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/feature/2011-film-awards-and-nominations |title=2011 Film Awards and Nominations |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS Interactive]] |date=2011-12-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114130517/http://www.metacritic.com/feature/2011-film-awards-and-nominations |archivedate=2012-11-14 |accessdate=2017-07-13 }}</ref>。尼可拉·溫丁·黑芬在[[第64屆坎城影展|第64屆坎城影展]]上憑此片獲得了[[最佳導演獎_(坎城影展)|最佳導演獎]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2011/may/23/entertainment/la-et-cannes-wrap-20110523 |first=Kenneth |last=Turran |title=Cannes: Festival Favorite Enjoys L.A. Ties |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2011-05-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004234635/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/may/23/entertainment/la-et-cannes-wrap-20110523 |archivedate=2013-10-04 |accessdate=2017-07-13 }}</ref>。《落日車神》也獲得了[[奧斯卡最佳音效剪輯獎|奧斯卡最佳音效剪輯獎]]的提名<ref name="Academy">{{Cite news |url=http://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2012 |title=The 84th Academy Awards (2012) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=2017-05-22 |work=[[美國電影藝術與科學學會|Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]] |publisher=AMPAS |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015232303/http://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2012 |archivedate=2014-10-15 }}</ref>。

