《落日車神》的電影原聲[[CD|CD]]於2011年9月27日由{{le|Lakeshore Records|Lakeshore Records}}發行<ref name="HRSoundtrack">{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/drive-soundtrack-released-231737 |title=''Drive'' Soundtrack To Be Released |first=Rebecca |last=Ford |work=The Hollywood Reporter |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |date=2011-09-06 |accessdate=2011-09-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110930152004/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/drive-soundtrack-released-231737 |archivedate=2011-09-30 }}</ref>，並由Edge Edge Film Scores所擁有<ref name="Drive">{{cite news |url=http://ce-fs.com/drive/ |title=''Drive'' Soundtrack on Cutting Edge Film Scores |first=Tom |last=Player |work=Stream "Drive Soundtrack" |publisher=Cutting Edge Music Holdings |date=2012-08-30 |accessdate=2012-08-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512103425/http://ce-fs.com/drive/ |archivedate=2013-05-12 }}</ref>。在此之前，由於在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上的病毒式評論，使得音樂在[[iTunes|iTunes]]上相當暢銷，其銷售值向上攀升至第四位<ref>{{cite news |last=Powers |first=Lindsay |title=''Drive'' Soundtrack Climbs iTunes Charts on Strong Viral Reviews |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/drive-soundtrack-climbs-itunes-charts-237175 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |date=2011-09-19 |accessdate=2011-09-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927032542/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/drive-soundtrack-climbs-itunes-charts-237175 |archivedate=2011-09-27 }}</ref>。該專輯於2012年6月由Mondo發行<ref>{{cite news |first=Justin |last=Ishmael |title=We Are Releasing The ''Drive'' Soundtrack on Vinyl! |url=http://blog.mondotees.com/2012/03/05/we-are-releasing-the-drive-soundtrack-on-vinyl/ |work=The Mondo Blog |date=2012-03-05 |accessdate=2012-03-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310064342/http://blog.mondotees.com/2012/03/05/we-are-releasing-the-drive-soundtrack-on-vinyl/ |archivedate=2012-03-10 }}</ref>。在當中的十九首歌曲都已獲得了好評。《{{le|波士頓先驅報|Boston Herald}}》的詹姆斯·維爾尼耶將其評為「A」，並認為該配樂在電影中的地位相當重要，根本難以想像沒有它的電影<ref name="BostonHerald">{{cite news |last=Verniere |first=James |title=''Drive'' soundtrack is worth hot pursuit |url=http://www.bostonherald.com/2011/09/%E2%80%98drive%E2%80%99_soundtrack_worth_hot_pursuit |work={{le|波士頓先驅報|Boston Herald|Boston Herald}} |publisher=Patrick J. Purcell |accessdate=2011-09-28 |archive-date=2017-06-22 |archive-url=https://archive.li/20170622184210/http://www.bostonherald.com/2011/09/%E2%80%98drive%E2%80%99_soundtrack_worth_hot_pursuit |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[Allmusic|Allmusic]]》的詹姆斯·克里斯多夫·蒙格特別喜歡開場曲「Nightcall」、「I Drive」、「Hammer」和「Bride of Deluxe」這幾首歌<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/drive-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-mw0002181261 |first=James Christopher |last=Monger |title=''Drive'' [Original Motion Picture Soundtrack] – Cliff Martinez |work=[[AllMusic|AllMusic]]. {{le|Rovi Corporation|Rovi Corporation}} |accessdate=2011-09-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120703025541/http://www.allmusic.com/album/drive-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-mw0002181261 |archivedate=2012-07-03 }}</ref>。《[[數碼間諜|數碼間諜]]》的梅爾·尼西姆給了它五分之四星的評價，他認為該配樂是以馬丁尼茲歌曲的形式開始播放，而不是去混合它，以獲得更加愉快的聽覺體驗<ref name="DS"/>。

2016年9月，Lakeshore和Invada Records發行了五週年特輯。同一個月，{{le|強尼·朱爾|Johnny Jewel}}、{{le|電氣青年 (樂團)|Electric Youth (band)|電氣青年}}和克里夫·馬丁尼茲討論了配樂和電影對他們的生活和當代音樂文化的影響。朱爾向《Vehlinggo》透露，《落日車神》的「聲音和視覺的混對現代旋律來說永遠是致命的。」<ref>{{cite news |first=Aaron |last=Vehling |title=''Drive'' at Five: Revisiting the Neon-Noir Masterpiece |url=https://vehlinggo.com/2016/09/07/drive-movie-fifth-anniversary-feature/ |work=Vehlinggo |date=2016-09-07 |accessdate=2016-11-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161214021221/https://vehlinggo.com/2016/09/07/drive-movie-fifth-anniversary-feature/ |archivedate=2016-12-14 }}</ref>該配樂被《[[Spin_(雜誌)|Spin]]》列入40首改編成另類音樂的電影原聲之一<ref>{{cite news |title=40 Movie Soundtracks That Changed Alternative Music |url=http://www.spin.com/2013/02/best-movie-soundtracks-list-scores-alternative-music/130208-drive/ |page=41 |accessdate=2017-05-20 |work=[[Spin_(雜誌)|Spin]] |publisher={{le|Eldridge Industries|Eldridge Industries}} |date=2013-02-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304042441/http://www.spin.com/2013/02/best-movie-soundtracks-list-scores-alternative-music/130208-drive/ |archivedate=2016-03-04 }}</ref>。

